(## 5. Core Technical Flow) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 5.1 Offline PCAP analysis flow) Tj
T*
(1. User uploads a `.pcap` or `.pcapng` file.) Tj
T*
(2. `PacketApiController` receives the file.) Tj
T*
(3. `PacketInspectionService` opens the capture using `pcap4j`.) Tj
T*
(4. Each packet is parsed and converted into a `PacketRecord`.) Tj
T*
(5. The service extracts:) Tj
T*
(   - source IP) Tj
T*
(   - destination IP) Tj
T*
(   - protocol) Tj
T*
(   - ports) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
